  "texts": [
    "The top three venues with respect to the number of remaining publications were The ACM Symposium on Eye Tracking Research and Applications, (ETRA) The ACM International Conference on Multimodal Interaction (ICMI), and Vision Research Journal.",
    "Moving forward, we present the different insights we extracted from the publications in the order of the ML workflow shown in Figure 6.",
    "However, we first discuss the research domains and learning tasks across the 77 publications.",
    "This step precedes the ML workflow but should help identify the current research state and possible challenges and gaps.",
    "We attached an Excel sheet as Supplementary material to this review, which includes all the information extraction phase details."
  ]
}